---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="Giving & Payments | YWAM Sendai"
  description="Support the mission of YWAM Sendai or make a school-related payment using approved methods for international and domestic transfers."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <div class="stack">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Giving & Payments</p>
          <h1 class="hero-title max-w-title">
            Support the mission or make a payment.
          </h1>
        </div>

        <p class="lead">
          YWAM Sendai depends on God’s provision through the generosity of churches,
          individuals, families, and partners. This page is also used for school-related
          payments and other approved transfers.
        </p>

        <div class="btn-group">
          <a
            href="https://buy.stripe.com/28EaEZgJcgATdIrer82Fa00"
            class="btn-primary"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Pay by Card
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/F2BWGTCV6H9P2"
            class="btn-secondary-dark"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Use PayPal
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:finance@ywamsendai.org" class="btn-secondary-dark">
            Contact Finance
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-inverse-soft mb-0">
          If you are unsure which method to use, please contact the finance team before sending money.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-dark stack-sm">
        <p class="eyebrow">Quick Guide</p>
        <h2 class="card-title">What this page is for</h2>
        <p>
          This page is for donations, project support, school-related payments,
          and other approved transfers using YWAM Sendai’s current payment methods.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why Giving Matters</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Financial partnership helps sustain the life and mission of the community</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Giving helps support ministry, training, hospitality, practical operations,
          and long-term service in Sendai and the wider Tohoku region.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Ministry and outreach</h3>
          <p>Supporting mission, discipleship, and service in real local contexts.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Training and community life</h3>
          <p>Helping sustain schools, hospitality, and shared rhythms of life together.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Long-term presence</h3>
          <p>Supporting faithful service in Sendai and the wider Tohoku region.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">What can this page be used for?</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Giving, project support, and practical payments</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-4">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">General donations</h3>
          <p>Support the wider life and mission of YWAM Sendai.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Project support</h3>
          <p>Support specific projects or needs where applicable.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">School-related payments</h3>
          <p>Use approved methods for tuition or other school-related costs.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">One-time or recurring giving</h3>
          <p>Depending on the method, one-time and repeat support may be possible.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Which payment method should I use?</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Choose the method that fits your location and situation</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          The best payment method depends on whether you are sending money from outside Japan,
          within Japan, or by card.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">If you are outside Japan</h3>
          <ul class="list-clean">
            <li><strong>Best option:</strong> Wise</li>
            <li><strong>Backup options:</strong> Stripe or PayPal</li>
            <li>Do not use direct international wire transfer</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">If you are in Japan</h3>
          <ul class="list-clean">
            <li><strong>Best option:</strong> Domestic bank transfer</li>
            <li><strong>Backup options:</strong> Stripe or PayPal</li>
            <li>Some school-related costs may need to be paid in cash in Japan</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Payment Methods</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Approved ways to send money</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-4">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Wise</h3>
          <p>Recommended for international payments. Usually the most cost-effective option.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Domestic bank transfer</h3>
          <p>The normal method for payments sent within Japan.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Stripe</h3>
          <p>A credit card option available as a backup method when needed.</p>
          <a
            href="https://buy.stripe.com/28EaEZgJcgATdIrer82Fa00"
            class="btn-text"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Open Stripe
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">PayPal</h3>
          <p>A backup option for payments or donations when other methods are not possible.</p>
          <a
            href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/F2BWGTCV6H9P2"
            class="btn-text"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Open PayPal
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="container-narrow" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <p class="text-soft">
          Wise is recommended for international payments. Domestic bank transfer is usually best within Japan.
          Stripe and PayPal are available as backup options, but fees may be higher.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Bank Details</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Use the correct account for your transfer</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          The correct account depends on whether you are sending money through Wise from outside Japan
          or making a domestic transfer within Japan.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">GMO Aozora Net Bank</h3>
          <p class="text-soft">Use for Wise transfers from outside Japan, or domestic transfers within Japan if preferred.</p>
          <ul class="list-clean">
            <li><strong>Bank Name:</strong> GMO Aozora Net Bank</li>
            <li><strong>Bank Code:</strong> 0310</li>
            <li><strong>Branch Name:</strong> Houjin</li>
            <li><strong>Branch Code:</strong> 101</li>
            <li><strong>Account Type:</strong> Savings / Futsuu</li>
            <li><strong>Account Number:</strong> 2042380</li>
            <li><strong>Account Name:</strong> セカイセイネンセンキョウカイ</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Japan Post Bank</h3>
          <p class="text-soft">Use for domestic transfers within Japan.</p>
          <ul class="list-clean">
            <li><strong>Bank Name:</strong> Japan Post Bank (ゆうちょ銀行)</li>
            <li><strong>Symbol (Kigo):</strong> 10140</li>
            <li><strong>Number (Bango):</strong> 65305041</li>
            <li><strong>Account Name:</strong> セカイセイネンセンキョウカイ</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="container-narrow" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <p class="text-soft">
          If you are sending money through Wise from outside Japan, use the GMO Aozora Net Bank account only.
          If you are unsure which account to use, contact finance@ywamsendai.org before sending money.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">After Sending a Payment</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Please notify the finance team</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          After making a payment or transfer, please notify YWAM Sendai so the finance team
          can identify and process it correctly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Send confirmation</h3>
          <p>Email the finance team after sending your payment or donation.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Use the right method</h3>
          <p>Check the current instructions carefully before sending money.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Ask if unsure</h3>
          <p>If you are unsure how your gift or payment should be directed, contact finance first.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper border-top">
    <div class="container container-narrow center stack">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Need Help?</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Questions about giving or payments?</h2>
        <p class="lead mx-auto">
          If you are unsure which method to use, need help with bank details,
          or want to confirm how a gift or payment should be directed, please contact the finance team.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
        <a href="mailto:finance@ywamsendai.org" class="btn-primary">Email Finance</a>
        <button type="button" class="btn-secondary open-hub-trigger">Ask AI</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>